name: A Blue Depth VII
description:
This piece is part of a series of mine (Under the Sea, 2017).

-

A diver descends into the depths of the ocean to explore new and mysterious creatures. Down in the dark, cold water, she is enveloped by a blue light.

-

Abstract light-painting created with steel wool on fire in pitch darkness. It was complemented by digital art.

*

'A Blue Depth VII', 2022
